<section id="reviews" class="reviews">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>Guest Reviews</h2>
      <p>See what our guests say about their stay in Phimai.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="reviews-grid">
      <div class="review-card">
        <div class="review-stars">
          <span>★★★★★</span>
        </div>
        <p>"Perfect location to explore Phimai Historical Park. The tiny home was cozy and had everything we needed. The free bikes were a great touch!"</p>
        <div class="reviewer">
          <strong>Sarah M.</strong>
          <span>March 2024</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="review-card">
        <div class="review-stars">
          <span>★★★★★</span>
        </div>
        <p>"Authentic Thai experience in a comfortable setting. The host was incredibly helpful and the tuktuk transfer made our departure so easy."</p>
        <div class="reviewer">
          <strong>James L.</strong>
          <span>February 2024</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="review-card">
        <div class="review-stars">
          <span>★★★★★</span>
        </div>
        <p>"Loved the small town atmosphere. Walking to Sai Ngam mangrove was beautiful. The kitchenette had everything we needed for our 4-day stay."</p>
        <div class="reviewer">
          <strong>Emma K.</strong>
          <span>January 2024</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .reviews {
    padding: 5rem 2rem;
    background: #FAFAFA;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .section-header h2 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #2C2C2C;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .section-header p {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: #5A5A5A;
    font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
  }

  .reviews-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .review-card {
    background: white;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  }

  .review-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
  }

  .review-stars {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .review-stars span {
    color: #FFD700;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
  }

  .review-card p {
    color: #5A5A5A;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .reviewer {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
  }

  .reviewer strong {
    color: #2C2C2C;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .reviewer span {
    color: #8A8A8A;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .reviews {
      padding: 3rem 1rem;
    }

    .section-header h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .reviews-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .review-card {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>